::Aerotaur::

"There is a base below us and I have business there anyway.  I'll see what I 
can do.  Of course I've never been there and the only reason I have business 
there is because it suddenly seemed important but let's go."  Aerotaur lands 
gracefully in front of the CF. Trying not to disturb Trinity too much he 
returns to his winged centaur mode.  He asks the people there "Hey can we get 
in I need to speak with ... actually I don't know who but I assume I will 
when I see them.  And we're kind of hungry."
